long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
See how far you’ve come this year. Every time you open a new tab, a progress bar will show you exactly how much of the year has flown by. It’s a simple way to stay motivated and appreciate the journey. Use this for daily motivation!

Relevant keywords: motivation, new tab extension, productivity extension, time management, year tracker, new tab page customization, progress bar
